title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Mar 28 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Mar 28 2022
description:
Biden calls for regime change in Russia, WH walks it back. Where are the calls for the 25th amendment? Chuck Todd laments Biden's new low in approval poll. Buck's midterm goal: 50 seats for the GOP. The Oscars slap heard round the world: Will Smith assaults Chris Rock on stage after joke about Jada Pinkett Smith. Caller says Will Smith wanted the publicity he's getting, C&B disagree.
